    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把这两个顶层状态和入口画出来。主动方和被动方各自有独立的子状态机吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Initiator",
        "Responder"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，Initiator内部有三个核心状态：InterestsSent、RangeSent和RangeRecv。流程是：先发送兴趣请求，收到响应后进入RangeSent，再收到范围响应后进入RangeRecv。",
